        <sourceInfo>
            <title>지구의친구,또다른지구가 있다면어떨까?</title>
            <author id="P20169" age="12" occupation="초등학생" sex="F" submission="오프라인" handwriting="Yes">개인글작성자</author>
        </sourceInfo>
